{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
Just as [C]long as You're the captain
As You're the captain of this vessel
When my [F]ship (when my battered ship)
Is lost at [C]sea (ship is lost at sea)
Then I [F]know (then I'll surely know)
I'll reach the [C]harbor (soon I'll reach the harbor)
When You calm (when you calm)
The [G7]storm for [C]me
{end_of_verse}
